					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I looked into the Tiny Toons cartoon maker for NES, and there's a large lookup table at CPU$FEDB that the game uses to fade arbitrary colors to color $02 and back, in 1/3 increments.
<br />
<br />When they generated this table, I wonder if they faded the colors in YIQ space, or if they interpolated to RGB and back.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />-Drag</div>
